1
00:01:42,455 --> 00:01:44,655
[GROWLING]

2
00:01:45,855 --> 00:01:49,155
[GRUNTING]

3
00:01:50,588 --> 00:01:55,088
- IRON REAPER SOUL STEALER!

4
00:01:55,122 --> 00:01:58,022
UGH!

5
00:02:02,055 --> 00:02:04,722
- OH, INUYASHA.

6
00:02:12,855 --> 00:02:14,955
[ROARING]

7
00:02:17,122 --> 00:02:18,155
- UGH!

8
00:02:18,188 --> 00:02:19,855
[ROARING]

9
00:02:19,888 --> 00:02:22,188
[GRUNTING]

10
00:02:23,722 --> 00:02:24,788
- AAH!

11
00:02:24,822 --> 00:02:26,655
AAH!

12
00:02:26,688 --> 00:02:28,155
[GROANING]

13
00:02:28,188 --> 00:02:29,755
- INUYASHA!

14
00:02:31,422 --> 00:02:32,588
[LAUGHTER]

15
00:02:32,622 --> 00:02:34,322
- NOW DO YOU UNDERSTAND?

16
00:02:34,355 --> 00:02:35,988
YOUR MEASURES ARE ALL IN VAIN.

17
00:02:36,022 --> 00:02:40,155
SURRENDER AND FIND A NEW HOME
INSIDE MY DEMON'S BELLY.

18
00:02:40,188 --> 00:02:41,022
[GROANING]

19
00:02:41,055 --> 00:02:43,088
- SO WHAT IF I CAN'T USE
THE TETSUSAIGA.

20
00:02:43,122 --> 00:02:47,955
I ONLY NEED ONE ARM TO TAKE OUT
THAT REPULSIVE DEMON!

21
00:02:47,988 --> 00:02:50,088
- HOLD YOUR TONGUE!

22
00:02:50,122 --> 00:02:52,755
[GROWLING AND ROARING]

23
00:02:52,788 --> 00:02:55,855
- BLADES OF BLOOD!

24
00:02:55,888 --> 00:02:58,255
[GROWLING]

25
00:03:00,722 --> 00:03:02,655
- HUH!

26
00:03:04,922 --> 00:03:06,888
[CHUCKLES]

27
00:03:06,922 --> 00:03:07,788
HMMPH!

28
00:03:07,822 --> 00:03:10,788
DON'T BE SO SURE
OF YOURSELF.

29
00:03:10,822 --> 00:03:12,722
[GROANING]

30
00:03:12,755 --> 00:03:15,288
- KAGOME!
- KAGOME!

31
00:03:15,322 --> 00:03:17,188
WHY, YOU--

32
00:03:17,222 --> 00:03:19,222
- DO NOT FORGET, INUYASHA.

33
00:03:19,255 --> 00:03:23,622
I HOLD KAGOME'S
VERY LIFE IN MY HAND.

34
00:03:24,555 --> 00:03:25,822
[SIGHS]

35
00:03:25,855 --> 00:03:27,888
[GROWLING]

36
00:03:31,688 --> 00:03:32,388
[ROARS]

37
00:03:32,422 --> 00:03:35,622
- DAMN!
WHAT AM I GOING TO DO?

38
00:03:37,355 --> 00:03:38,622
- ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

39
00:03:38,655 --> 00:03:40,622
ARE YOU IN PAIN, KAGOME?

40
00:03:40,655 --> 00:03:42,688
- YEAH, BUT I'M FINE, SANGO.

41
00:03:42,722 --> 00:03:44,855
DON'T WORRY ABOUT ME.

42
00:03:44,888 --> 00:03:46,122
[MOANS]

43
00:03:46,155 --> 00:03:47,222
- COME ON, MIROKU.

44
00:03:47,255 --> 00:03:48,955
WE HAVE TO HELP INUYASHA.

45
00:03:48,988 --> 00:03:51,888
KAGOME WON'T BE ABLE
TO LAST FOR VERY LONG.

46
00:03:51,922 --> 00:03:52,722
- HOLD ON.

47
00:03:52,755 --> 00:03:54,855
I FIGURE TSUBAKI INTENDS
TO KILL KAGOME

48
00:03:54,888 --> 00:03:58,388
WHETHER INUYASHA WINS
OR LOSES THIS BATTLE.

49
00:03:58,422 --> 00:03:59,655
- YOU MEAN--
- RIGHT.

50
00:03:59,688 --> 00:04:03,888
OUR ONLY HOPE IS TO FIND A WAY
TO BREAK TSUBAKI'S CURSE.

51
00:04:03,922 --> 00:04:05,888
EITHER WE DESTROY TSUBAKI

52
00:04:05,922 --> 00:04:09,155
OR WE KILL SHIKIGAMI,
HER DEMON PUPPET.

53
00:04:09,188 --> 00:04:10,322
- WAIT A MINUTE.

54
00:04:10,355 --> 00:04:12,355
REMEMBER JUST BEFORE
KAGOME FELL ILL,

55
00:04:12,388 --> 00:04:14,022
SHE SAID SHE'D BEEN
BITTEN AT THE WELL.

56
00:04:14,055 --> 00:04:18,822
- EXACTLY. IT WAS MORE THAN
LIKELY THAT DEMON SERPENT.

57
00:04:18,855 --> 00:04:21,455
I'M ALMOST SURE OF IT.

58
00:04:21,488 --> 00:04:23,055
BACK ME UP, SANGO!

59
00:04:23,088 --> 00:04:24,688
- YOU CAN COUNT ON IT!

60
00:04:24,722 --> 00:04:26,188
[PANTING]

61
00:04:26,222 --> 00:04:27,855
[GROWLING]

62
00:04:27,888 --> 00:04:29,455
- AAH! AAH!

63
00:04:29,488 --> 00:04:31,922
- HIRAIKOTSU!

64
00:04:31,955 --> 00:04:34,222
[GROWLING]

65
00:04:34,255 --> 00:04:37,288
[PANTING]

66
00:04:37,322 --> 00:04:38,722
- HYAH!

67
00:04:38,755 --> 00:04:39,588
[CHUCKLES]

68
00:04:39,622 --> 00:04:43,122
- EXORCISM SUTRAS.
THEY'RE USELESS ON ME!

69
00:04:43,155 --> 00:04:45,222
[ROARS]

70
00:04:46,755 --> 00:04:48,055
- OHH!

71
00:04:48,088 --> 00:04:51,522
- FOOL!
MY CURSE CANNOT BE BROKEN!

72
00:04:51,555 --> 00:04:54,088
[GRUNTING]

73
00:04:54,122 --> 00:04:55,155
- AAH!

74
00:04:55,188 --> 00:04:56,422
OH, NO!

75
00:04:56,455 --> 00:04:57,822
[ROARS]

76
00:04:57,855 --> 00:04:59,988
- MIROKU!

77
00:05:00,022 --> 00:05:02,255
- YOU SEEM TO ENJOY PAIN.

78
00:05:02,288 --> 00:05:04,755
JUST REMEMBER,
THE LONGER YOU RESIST ME,

79
00:05:04,788 --> 00:05:07,788
THE LONGER HER SUFFERING
WILL BE PROLONGED.

80
00:05:07,822 --> 00:05:10,388
[GROANING]

81
00:05:10,422 --> 00:05:12,188
IT WOULD BE SO EASY TO END.

82
00:05:12,222 --> 00:05:18,122
SHALL I SEND KAGOME TO HER
DEMISE THIS VERY INSTANT?

83
00:05:18,155 --> 00:05:20,188
- AAH!

84
00:05:20,222 --> 00:05:21,255
- KAGOME!

85
00:05:21,288 --> 00:05:23,322
KAGOME,
YOU'VE GOT TO BE STRONG!

86
00:05:23,355 --> 00:05:27,355
KAGOME! SAY SOMETHING!

87
00:05:31,488 --> 00:05:32,555
- I HEAR YOU, SANGO.

88
00:05:32,588 --> 00:05:34,788
I'LL WAKE UP IN A MINUTE.

89
00:05:34,822 --> 00:05:36,722
WAIT FOR ME.

90
00:05:36,755 --> 00:05:38,755
[ALARM RINGING]

91
00:05:39,622 --> 00:05:41,455
WHAT'S THAT SOUND?

92
00:05:41,488 --> 00:05:43,255
IT'S SO NOISY.

93
00:05:43,288 --> 00:05:46,455
- KAGOME? KAGOME!
KAGOME!

94
00:05:46,488 --> 00:05:48,955
- SOMEONE'S CALLING ME.

95
00:05:48,988 --> 00:05:49,955
WHO IS IT?

96
00:05:49,988 --> 00:05:51,288
I CAN'T REMEMBER.

97
00:05:51,322 --> 00:05:54,988
- KAGOME, WAKE UP
OR YOU'LL BE LATE FOR SCHOOL.

98
00:05:55,022 --> 00:05:55,888
- HUH?

99
00:05:55,922 --> 00:05:56,788
[ALARM STOPS]

100
00:05:56,822 --> 00:06:00,688
YOU CAN'T STAY IN BED
FOREVER, YOUNG LADY.

101
00:06:00,722 --> 00:06:01,555
[GASPS]

102
00:06:01,588 --> 00:06:05,322
- WHAT HAPPENED TO SANGO?
AND INUYASHA?

103
00:06:05,355 --> 00:06:06,955
AND MIROKU?

104
00:06:06,988 --> 00:06:10,188
HOW THE HECK DID I END UP
BACK IN THIS WORLD?

105
00:06:10,222 --> 00:06:13,288
- SOUNDS LIKE QUITE THE DREAM.

106
00:06:14,388 --> 00:06:16,122
HURRY AND COME DOWNSTAIRS.

107
00:06:16,155 --> 00:06:18,555
BREAKFAST WILL
BE READY FOR YOU.

108
00:06:18,588 --> 00:06:20,555
- HUH?

109
00:06:24,555 --> 00:06:27,222
- OH, GOOD MORNING, KAGOME.

110
00:06:28,888 --> 00:06:29,822
- HONESTLY, GIRL.

111
00:06:29,855 --> 00:06:32,455
CAN'T YOU AT LEAST
SAY "GOOD MORNING"?

112
00:06:32,488 --> 00:06:34,322
- MORNING.

113
00:06:34,355 --> 00:06:35,288
HANG ON.

114
00:06:35,322 --> 00:06:38,855
CAN YOU TELL ME WHEN EXACTLY
I CAME BACK HERE?

115
00:06:38,888 --> 00:06:39,888
- BACK WHERE?

116
00:06:39,922 --> 00:06:42,255
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN?
DID YOU GO SOMEWHERE?

117
00:06:42,288 --> 00:06:44,922
- YOU KNOW.
WHERE I'M ALWAYS GOING.

118
00:06:44,955 --> 00:06:46,188
THE OTHER DIMENSION?

119
00:06:46,222 --> 00:06:49,322
500 YEARS IN THE PAST.
REMEMBER?

120
00:06:49,355 --> 00:06:50,988
WHEN I GO DOWN THAT
OLD, HIDDEN WELL,

121
00:06:51,022 --> 00:06:55,455
I END UP BACK IN THE FEUDAL ERA
WHERE THERE ARE TONS OF DEMONS.

122
00:06:55,488 --> 00:06:58,688
- OH! YOU WENT
INTO THAT WELL?

123
00:06:58,722 --> 00:07:01,655
- DUH! ONLY ABOUT
100 TIMES ALREADY.

124
00:07:01,688 --> 00:07:04,688
INUYASHA CAME HERE, TOO,
REMEMBER?

125
00:07:04,722 --> 00:07:05,822
- INUYASHA?

126
00:07:05,855 --> 00:07:07,222
- WHAT ON EARTH IS THAT?

127
00:07:07,255 --> 00:07:09,455
- YOU MEAN, YOU'VE
FORGOTTEN ABOUT HIM?

128
00:07:09,488 --> 00:07:11,322
GRAMPS, ARE YOU FEELING OK?

129
00:07:11,355 --> 00:07:15,155
YOU KNOW, HE'S THE GUY
WITH THE DOG EARS.

130
00:07:15,188 --> 00:07:16,555
- HMM.

131
00:07:16,588 --> 00:07:18,988
- ARE YOU SURE
YOU'RE ALL RIGHT?

132
00:07:19,022 --> 00:07:20,022
- NO KIDDING!

133
00:07:20,055 --> 00:07:22,922
MAYBE YOU SHOULD STAY HOME
FROM SCHOOL TODAY, SIS.

134
00:07:22,955 --> 00:07:25,988
- SHE'S STILL HALF ASLEEP.

135
00:07:27,588 --> 00:07:29,355
- OH, DEAR.

136
00:07:29,388 --> 00:07:31,255
[ALL SIGH]

137
00:07:37,455 --> 00:07:39,122
NO WAY.

138
00:07:39,155 --> 00:07:42,855
- KAGOME, YOU'LL BE
LATE FOR SCHOOL!

139
00:07:42,888 --> 00:07:44,555
- WHAT'S GOING ON?

140
00:07:44,588 --> 00:07:48,188
HAS THIS WHOLE THING
BEEN JUST A DREAM?

141
00:07:51,222 --> 00:07:53,322
- WHAT'S THE MATTER
WITH YOU, KAGOME?

142
00:07:53,355 --> 00:07:54,355
- YOU SEEM KIND OF DOWN.

143
00:07:54,388 --> 00:07:57,022
- WELL...
- YOU'VE GOT A PROBLEM?

144
00:07:57,055 --> 00:07:59,755
- LIKE...BOYFRIEND TROUBLE?

145
00:07:59,788 --> 00:08:01,222
- BOYFRIEND?

146
00:08:01,255 --> 00:08:02,188
THAT'S RIGHT!

147
00:08:02,222 --> 00:08:04,888
YOU GUYS ALL REMEMBER
MY BOYFRIEND, DON'T YOU?

148
00:08:04,922 --> 00:08:06,955
- WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?
SURE WE DO.

149
00:08:06,988 --> 00:08:09,722
- YES! IT WASN'T
A DREAM AFTER ALL!

150
00:08:09,755 --> 00:08:12,788
- IT'S HOJO!
HE'S IN GROUP "B."

151
00:08:12,822 --> 00:08:13,655
[LAUGHTER]

152
00:08:13,688 --> 00:08:15,155
[SIGHS WITH FRUSTRATION]

153
00:08:15,188 --> 00:08:16,422
- DUH! REMEMBER?

154
00:08:16,455 --> 00:08:19,988
ATTITUDE MAN?
YOU KNOW, MR. POSSESSIVE?

155
00:08:20,022 --> 00:08:21,055
- WHO'S THAT?

156
00:08:21,088 --> 00:08:23,255
YOU WERE TWO-TIMING ON HOJO?

157
00:08:23,288 --> 00:08:24,388
- NO! NO! NO!

158
00:08:24,422 --> 00:08:27,555
- WOW, YOU SURE GO FOR IT!

159
00:08:28,422 --> 00:08:30,988
[SIGHS]
HUH?

160
00:08:35,955 --> 00:08:36,922
- I DON'T GET IT.

161
00:08:36,955 --> 00:08:41,555
SUDDENLY I'VE BEEN THRUST
BACK INTO MY OLD LIFE.

162
00:08:42,322 --> 00:08:43,555
- HIGURASHI.

163
00:08:43,588 --> 00:08:44,455
- YES?

164
00:08:44,488 --> 00:08:48,622
- READ THE NEXT PART.
- OK.

165
00:08:48,655 --> 00:08:49,522
UH...

166
00:08:49,555 --> 00:08:51,955
- WHAT'S THE MATTER NOW?
- I DON'T GET IT.

167
00:08:51,988 --> 00:08:54,022
- ENTRANCE EXAMS
ARE COMING UP SOON.

168
00:08:54,055 --> 00:08:57,655
YOU BETTER START
PAYING ATTENTION.

169
00:08:57,688 --> 00:08:59,522
[SIGHS]

170
00:08:59,555 --> 00:09:01,022
- ENTRANCE EXAMS.

171
00:09:01,055 --> 00:09:04,022
YEAH, I'M SUPPOSED
TO STUDY FOR EXAMS.

172
00:09:04,055 --> 00:09:05,622
THAT'S MY REAL LIFE.

173
00:09:05,655 --> 00:09:08,888
THAT WAS HOW I WANTED
MY LIFE TO BE.

174
00:09:08,922 --> 00:09:11,488
BUT THEN...

175
00:09:13,055 --> 00:09:15,188
- KAGOME!

176
00:09:15,222 --> 00:09:16,355
- HUH?

177
00:09:16,388 --> 00:09:17,522
- HEY. YOU.

178
00:09:17,555 --> 00:09:19,888
- HERE.
I GOT SOMETHING FOR YOU.

179
00:09:19,922 --> 00:09:22,488
THIS WILL CHEER YOU UP
AND WORK WONDERS

180
00:09:22,522 --> 00:09:24,922
ON THE ACUPRESSURE POINTS
OF YOUR SOLES.

181
00:09:24,955 --> 00:09:27,788
ONE STEP AND YOU'LL BE SOLD.

182
00:09:27,822 --> 00:09:28,855
[CHUCKLES]

183
00:09:28,888 --> 00:09:29,888
- SOMETHING'S WRONG.

184
00:09:29,922 --> 00:09:33,488
I JUST KNOW THIS ISN'T
THE WAY IT'S SUPPOSED TO BE.

185
00:09:34,988 --> 00:09:37,555
- I WANT TO HAVE LOTS OF KIDS.

186
00:09:37,588 --> 00:09:39,988
- YOU'RE SUCH A JOKER.

187
00:09:48,322 --> 00:09:51,288
- GRANDMA, BUY ME
A SACRED JEWEL KEY HOLDER.

188
00:09:51,322 --> 00:09:54,488
- SURE.
- THE SACRED JEWEL, YOU SAY.

189
00:09:54,522 --> 00:09:55,522
- SACRED JEWEL?

190
00:09:55,555 --> 00:09:57,855
- I BET YOU'VE NEVER HEARD
THE ORIGIN OF THE JEWEL.

191
00:09:57,888 --> 00:09:59,488
MY OWN GRANDFATHER...

192
00:09:59,522 --> 00:10:01,722
- HA HA!
LET'S GO, GRANDMA.

193
00:10:01,755 --> 00:10:02,755
- ALL RIGHT.

194
00:10:02,788 --> 00:10:05,022
- ...LONG AGO,
DEEP IN THE MOUNTAINS

195
00:10:05,055 --> 00:10:07,588
WHERE MANY FEAR TO TREAD...
[KAGOME GROANING]

196
00:10:07,622 --> 00:10:11,588
HELLO?
WHERE'D EVERYBODY GO?

197
00:10:16,922 --> 00:10:18,788
[MOANS]

198
00:10:23,222 --> 00:10:25,322
[CAT MEOWING]

199
00:10:25,355 --> 00:10:27,222
- HUH?

200
00:10:27,255 --> 00:10:31,322
BUYO, I THINK THERE MIGHT BE
SOMETHING WRONG WITH ME.

201
00:10:31,355 --> 00:10:32,888
[CAT GRUMBLES]

202
00:10:32,922 --> 00:10:38,388
THERE ARE JUST SO MANY THINGS
RACING AROUND INSIDE MY HEAD.

203
00:10:38,422 --> 00:10:41,955
IT FEELS LIKE I WAS SUPPOSED TO
BE DOING SOMETHING RIGHT NOW,

204
00:10:41,988 --> 00:10:44,322
BUT I CAN'T THINK
OF WHAT IT WAS.

205
00:10:44,355 --> 00:10:46,988
[CAT GRUMBLES]

206
00:10:52,088 --> 00:10:58,822
THINGS I FEEL LIKE I SHOULD
REMEMBER ARE SLOWLY FADING AWAY.

207
00:11:00,355 --> 00:11:02,788
[BELL DINGING]

208
00:11:02,988 --> 00:11:08,688
I HAVE THIS FEELING THAT
WHAT I'M DOING NOW IS WRONG.

209
00:11:10,822 --> 00:11:14,855
BUT WHAT IS IT THAT
I'M SUPPOSED TO DO?

210
00:11:21,288 --> 00:11:25,722
I'M GETTING USED TO THIS PAIN
I SOMETIMES GET IN MY NECK.

211
00:11:25,755 --> 00:11:29,922
AND NOW I HARDLY
EVEN WORRY ABOUT IT.

212
00:11:37,222 --> 00:11:38,855
WHO AM I?

213
00:11:38,888 --> 00:11:40,755
AND WHY AM I HERE?

214
00:11:40,788 --> 00:11:41,988
WHAT AM I DOING?

215
00:11:42,022 --> 00:11:47,822
HOW COME I FEEL SO ANXIOUS
AND SO UNCERTAIN?

216
00:11:49,222 --> 00:11:50,788
[GASPS]

217
00:11:50,822 --> 00:11:52,955
- WHAT'S WRONG, KAGOME?

218
00:11:52,988 --> 00:11:56,588
- I'M SORRY.
I GOT TO GO, HOJO!

219
00:11:56,622 --> 00:11:58,788
- KAGOME?

220
00:12:01,222 --> 00:12:03,788
ALL RIGHT, NEXT UP.

221
00:12:04,955 --> 00:12:08,622
OH, YOU'VE FINALLY ARRIVED.

222
00:12:08,655 --> 00:12:11,055
- UH, I, UH...

223
00:12:11,088 --> 00:12:13,322
- WOULD YOU LIKE TO TRY?

224
00:12:13,355 --> 00:12:14,088
- HUH?

225
00:12:14,122 --> 00:12:17,755
- ISN'T THAT WHY YOU'VE COME?

226
00:12:18,988 --> 00:12:20,455
- MM-HMM.

227
00:12:20,488 --> 00:12:22,255
- AIM FOR THAT TARGET.

228
00:12:22,288 --> 00:12:23,655
TAKE YOUR TIME.

229
00:12:23,688 --> 00:12:25,388
- ALL RIGHT.

230
00:12:27,855 --> 00:12:29,988
- YOUR LINE IS GOOD.

231
00:12:30,022 --> 00:12:32,488
- HIT THE MARK.

232
00:12:33,955 --> 00:12:36,155
- YOU NEED MORE PRACTICE.

233
00:12:36,188 --> 00:12:38,488
YOUR CONCENTRATION IS LACKING.

234
00:12:38,522 --> 00:12:40,988
- EXCUSE ME.
WHO EXACTLY--

235
00:12:41,022 --> 00:12:42,855
- WHO ARE YOU?
- UH!

236
00:12:42,888 --> 00:12:45,222
- WHO ARE YOU?

237
00:12:45,255 --> 00:12:48,388
- ME? I'M, UH...

238
00:12:48,422 --> 00:12:52,388
- ARE YOU...
ARE YOU ME?

239
00:12:52,422 --> 00:12:57,222
WATCH YOURSELF, OR YOU'LL END UP
KILLING INUYASHA AGAIN.

240
00:12:57,255 --> 00:12:58,988
- INUYASHA?

241
00:12:59,022 --> 00:13:00,588
[GROANS]

242
00:13:00,622 --> 00:13:02,222
- KAGOME!

243
00:13:02,255 --> 00:13:03,322
[MOANING]

244
00:13:03,355 --> 00:13:06,188
COME ON.
HANG IN THERE, KAGOME.

245
00:13:06,222 --> 00:13:07,955
[ROARING]

246
00:13:07,988 --> 00:13:10,255
[GRUNTING]

247
00:13:11,655 --> 00:13:14,455
- IN...INUYASHA!

248
00:13:14,488 --> 00:13:17,122
[MOANING]
WAIT!

249
00:13:17,155 --> 00:13:20,488
I HAVE TO GET UP
FROM THIS WORLD!

250
00:13:22,155 --> 00:13:23,888
- HMMPH!

251
00:13:23,922 --> 00:13:25,088
- WAIT, I SAID!

252
00:13:25,122 --> 00:13:26,422
NO! PLEASE, STOP!

253
00:13:26,455 --> 00:13:28,322
WAIT, I SAID!
COME BACK HERE!

254
00:13:28,355 --> 00:13:30,955
PLEASE, STOP!

255
00:13:30,988 --> 00:13:32,522
- TELL ME WHO YOU ARE.

256
00:13:32,555 --> 00:13:33,688
- THAT ISN'T IMPORTANT NOW!

257
00:13:33,722 --> 00:13:35,622
- THIS IS A WORLD
OF YOUR OWN MAKING.

258
00:13:35,655 --> 00:13:38,355
YOU HAVE DECIDED
WHO YOU ARE.

259
00:13:38,388 --> 00:13:40,355
NOW, ANSWER ME!

260
00:13:40,388 --> 00:13:42,188
TELL ME WHO YOU ARE!

261
00:13:42,222 --> 00:13:43,455
[MOANS]

262
00:13:43,488 --> 00:13:44,688
- KAGOME!

263
00:13:44,722 --> 00:13:46,455
- INUYASHA!

264
00:13:46,488 --> 00:13:48,888
[GRUNTING]

265
00:13:50,288 --> 00:13:52,622
[GROWLS]

266
00:13:54,955 --> 00:13:56,688
- AAH!

267
00:13:56,722 --> 00:13:59,522
UGH!

268
00:13:59,555 --> 00:14:02,855
[GROWLING]

269
00:14:02,888 --> 00:14:05,022
- INUYASHA!

270
00:14:06,622 --> 00:14:08,722
[ROARING]

271
00:14:09,855 --> 00:14:11,722
- WHAT?

272
00:14:14,722 --> 00:14:16,022
[GASPS]

273
00:14:16,055 --> 00:14:19,022
[PANTING]

274
00:14:19,888 --> 00:14:23,722
WENCH! WHY ARE YOU
STILL ABLE TO MOVE?

275
00:14:23,755 --> 00:14:24,622
- WELL, I CAN.

276
00:14:24,655 --> 00:14:26,922
MAYBE YOU'RE NOT
CONCENTRATING HARD ENOUGH.

277
00:14:26,955 --> 00:14:30,755
- HUH! WELL, YOU'VE CERTAINLY
MANAGED TO ENDURE MY SPELL.

278
00:14:30,788 --> 00:14:36,722
SO IT WOULD SEEM THAT
YOU TRULY ARE KIKYO'S
REINCARNATION AFTER ALL.

279
00:14:36,755 --> 00:14:40,255
ALTHOUGH...IF YOU ACTUALLY
WERE THE REAL KIKYO,

280
00:14:40,288 --> 00:14:43,555
THAT ARROW MOST CERTAINLY
WOULDN'T HAVE MISSED ME,

281
00:14:43,588 --> 00:14:46,988
MEANING YOU'RE
AN IMITATION KIKYO.

282
00:14:47,022 --> 00:14:49,888
- YOU'LL REGRET THAT.

283
00:14:49,922 --> 00:14:52,555
- TELL ME WHO YOU ARE.

284
00:14:52,588 --> 00:14:54,388
- I AM KAGOME!

285
00:14:54,422 --> 00:14:57,422
I'M NOT ANYONE ELSE!

286
00:15:04,022 --> 00:15:06,288
- HMM.

287
00:15:14,022 --> 00:15:15,422
- HMMPH!

288
00:15:15,455 --> 00:15:17,322
- YOU ARE FOOLISH,

289
00:15:17,355 --> 00:15:20,155
RUSHING TO YOUR DEATH.

290
00:15:21,655 --> 00:15:24,322
[HISSES]

291
00:15:25,522 --> 00:15:28,322
[GROANING AND CHOKING]

292
00:15:30,055 --> 00:15:31,422
- KAGOME!

293
00:15:31,455 --> 00:15:33,088
- KAGOME!
- OHH!

294
00:15:33,122 --> 00:15:35,255
[GROANING]

295
00:15:36,822 --> 00:15:39,155
[ROARING]

296
00:15:39,188 --> 00:15:40,655
- AAH!

297
00:15:52,957 --> 00:15:54,624
- KAGOME!

298
00:15:55,424 --> 00:15:59,090
[MOANING]
- SHE WON'T LAST MUCH LONGER.

299
00:16:00,057 --> 00:16:02,690
[GRUNTING]

300
00:16:02,990 --> 00:16:06,490
- KAGOME...JUST BE
STRONG A BIT LONGER.

301
00:16:06,524 --> 00:16:08,124
- YEAH, SURE.

302
00:16:08,157 --> 00:16:10,090
I CAN HANG ON A WHILE.

303
00:16:10,124 --> 00:16:11,724
- KAGOME.

304
00:16:11,757 --> 00:16:14,057
- I'VE HAD ENOUGH OF YOU TWO!

305
00:16:14,090 --> 00:16:16,290
[GROWLING]

306
00:16:18,424 --> 00:16:21,824
- I'LL NEVER LET YOU KILL HER!

307
00:16:22,357 --> 00:16:25,190
YOU BETTER STAY
OUT OF MY WAY!

308
00:16:25,224 --> 00:16:28,524
IRON REAPER SOUL STEALER!

309
00:16:28,557 --> 00:16:29,657
HYAH!

310
00:16:29,690 --> 00:16:32,490
[GAGGING]

311
00:16:35,490 --> 00:16:37,724
THIS IS THE END, TSUBAKI!

312
00:16:37,757 --> 00:16:39,524
[GASPING]

313
00:16:42,290 --> 00:16:44,457
- WELL DONE, INUYASHA!

314
00:16:44,490 --> 00:16:46,490
[GRUNTS]

315
00:16:52,524 --> 00:16:53,290
ONE DOWN.

316
00:16:53,324 --> 00:16:56,357
- SORRY ABOUT YOUR
SERPENT, TSUBAKI.

317
00:16:56,390 --> 00:16:58,357
- HA HA HA!
YOU'RE NAIVE.

318
00:16:58,390 --> 00:17:01,790
DO YOU HONESTLY THINK
THE CURSE HAS BEEN BROKEN?

319
00:17:01,824 --> 00:17:02,724
- WHAT?

320
00:17:02,757 --> 00:17:05,924
- THE SPELL STILL
HOLDS, YOU FOOL.

321
00:17:05,957 --> 00:17:07,924
- HUH?
- HUH?

322
00:17:09,090 --> 00:17:11,790
[GROANING]

323
00:17:11,824 --> 00:17:13,224
- SHE'S NOT RECOVERING,

324
00:17:13,257 --> 00:17:15,724
EVEN THOUGH SHIKIGAMI
WAS DESTROYED.

325
00:17:15,757 --> 00:17:18,490
- KAGOME WILL DIE.

326
00:17:18,524 --> 00:17:22,657
OH, YES.
AND THE REST OF YOU.

327
00:17:25,657 --> 00:17:27,457
- HUH?

328
00:17:28,590 --> 00:17:31,224
[DEMONS ROARING]

329
00:17:31,257 --> 00:17:32,557
UGH!

330
00:17:32,590 --> 00:17:34,724
AHH!

331
00:17:34,757 --> 00:17:36,090
HUH?

332
00:17:36,124 --> 00:17:39,890
- SHE HAD MORE
DEMONS INSIDE HER!

333
00:17:39,924 --> 00:17:42,524
- DAMN THAT WITCH TO HELL!

334
00:17:42,557 --> 00:17:45,024
[GRUNTING]

335
00:17:49,990 --> 00:17:54,124
- KIRARA, STAY HERE
AND PROTECT KAGOME.

336
00:17:55,157 --> 00:17:57,357
HIRAIKOTSU!

337
00:17:59,357 --> 00:18:02,157
- UGH! HYAH!

338
00:18:10,290 --> 00:18:11,590
[GRASS RUSTLING]

339
00:18:11,624 --> 00:18:12,857
- HUH?

340
00:18:12,890 --> 00:18:13,524
- HMM.

341
00:18:13,557 --> 00:18:16,857
- SHIKIGAMI!
IT COULDN'T BE!

342
00:18:20,724 --> 00:18:22,790
- UGH! DAMN IT!

343
00:18:22,824 --> 00:18:24,890
THESE DEMONS WERE
JUST A DIVERSION!

344
00:18:24,924 --> 00:18:27,757
- CORRECT, BUT NOW
IT'S FAR TOO LATE!

345
00:18:27,790 --> 00:18:29,024
SHIKIGAMI!

346
00:18:29,057 --> 00:18:29,890
BITE OFF THAT WOMAN'S HEAD

347
00:18:29,924 --> 00:18:33,424
AND GET THE SACRED
JEWEL SHARDS FROM HER!

348
00:18:33,457 --> 00:18:34,424
- KAGOME!

349
00:18:34,457 --> 00:18:37,557
DAMN IT! I WON'T MAKE IT
TO HER IN TIME!

350
00:18:37,590 --> 00:18:40,190
[GROANING]

351
00:18:41,590 --> 00:18:44,824
- NOT THIS TIME, SCALY!

352
00:18:44,857 --> 00:18:46,824
YOU BIT ME BY THE WELL.

353
00:18:46,857 --> 00:18:49,357
YOU WON'T GET ME AGAIN!

354
00:18:51,490 --> 00:18:52,457
NO CHANCE!

355
00:18:52,490 --> 00:18:56,857
THIS TIME...
VICTORY IS MINE!

356
00:19:00,990 --> 00:19:02,524
- OH, NO!

357
00:19:02,557 --> 00:19:06,690
AAH!

358
00:19:06,724 --> 00:19:08,290
[GASPING]

359
00:19:08,324 --> 00:19:10,290
- SHE THREW THE SERPENT AT HER!

360
00:19:10,324 --> 00:19:13,124
- SHE SENT MY CURSE
BACK TO ME,

361
00:19:13,157 --> 00:19:14,690
JUST AS KIKYO DID!

362
00:19:14,724 --> 00:19:17,757
JUST LIKE THAT LAST TIME!

363
00:19:20,324 --> 00:19:22,224
[HISSING]

364
00:19:25,757 --> 00:19:26,624
[GASP]

365
00:19:26,657 --> 00:19:30,790
[SCREAMING]

366
00:19:33,424 --> 00:19:38,290
WHY MUST I BE DONE IN
BY THAT YOUNG WENCH?

367
00:19:41,524 --> 00:19:43,290
[SIGHING]

368
00:19:44,290 --> 00:19:44,990
[GASP]

369
00:19:45,024 --> 00:19:47,990
THE JEWEL IS BEGINNING
TO PURIFY!

370
00:19:51,724 --> 00:19:53,957
[SHATTERING]

371
00:19:54,857 --> 00:19:56,790
- THE SHARDS HAVE COME OUT!

372
00:19:56,824 --> 00:19:58,557
- IT CAN'T BE!

373
00:19:58,590 --> 00:20:01,390
[GRUNTING]

374
00:20:01,424 --> 00:20:04,290
WHY, YOU--

375
00:20:05,957 --> 00:20:07,490
- SHE'S GETTING AWAY!

376
00:20:07,524 --> 00:20:08,390
- NOT FROM ME!

377
00:20:08,424 --> 00:20:10,990
I'M NOT FINISHED WITH YOU YET!

378
00:20:11,024 --> 00:20:12,790
HA!

379
00:20:19,590 --> 00:20:21,824
- NO! NO!

380
00:20:30,224 --> 00:20:33,290
- DAMN! SHE GOT AWAY.

381
00:20:35,757 --> 00:20:36,957
KAGOME!

382
00:20:36,990 --> 00:20:39,424
[GROANING]

383
00:20:39,457 --> 00:20:43,257
- INU...YASHA.

384
00:20:44,590 --> 00:20:45,624
- SO, IS THAT IT?

385
00:20:45,657 --> 00:20:48,690
YOU INTEND TO LET HER LEAVE
WITH YOUR SACRED JEWEL?

386
00:20:48,724 --> 00:20:52,390
- OF COURSE NOT.
I'LL SOON GET IT BACK.

387
00:20:52,424 --> 00:20:54,657
BESIDES...
- BESIDES WHAT?

388
00:20:54,690 --> 00:20:58,057
- I MUST GIVE THE DARK
PRIESTESS THE OPPORTUNITY

389
00:20:58,090 --> 00:20:59,857
TO SEEK HER REVENGE.

390
00:20:59,890 --> 00:21:00,890
[SCOFFS]

391
00:21:00,924 --> 00:21:03,857
- HOW VERY KIND AND
CONSIDERATE OF YOU.

392
00:21:03,890 --> 00:21:05,757
- HMM.

393
00:21:14,524 --> 00:21:16,090
- MY POWERS HAVE WANED,

394
00:21:16,124 --> 00:21:20,457
AND THANKS TO THOSE FOOLS,
MY DEMONS HAVE ALL PERISHED.

395
00:21:20,490 --> 00:21:22,357
I WAS SO CLOSE TO VICTORY.

396
00:21:22,390 --> 00:21:25,890
AT LEAST I'LL BE ABLE
TO INCREASE MY POWERS IMMENSELY

397
00:21:25,924 --> 00:21:29,224
WITH A SACRED JEWEL THIS LARGE.

398
00:21:31,857 --> 00:21:34,124
I'LL DEFEAT YOU NEXT TIME.

399
00:21:34,157 --> 00:21:36,590
I'LL GET REVENGE
FOR THIS HUMILIATION,

400
00:21:36,624 --> 00:21:39,790
INUYASHA AND KAGOME!

401
00:21:44,757 --> 00:21:47,524
- KAGOME MUST BE SO TIRED.

402
00:21:47,557 --> 00:21:48,457
- CAN'T BLAME HER.

403
00:21:48,490 --> 00:21:51,490
SHE WAS UNDER A SPELL
FOR SO LONG.

404
00:21:52,357 --> 00:21:53,890
- INUYASHA! KAGOME!

405
00:21:53,924 --> 00:21:55,490
OVER HERE!
HA HA HA HA!

406
00:21:55,524 --> 00:21:56,957
- I'M SORRY, KAGOME.

407
00:21:56,990 --> 00:22:00,057
THIS ONLY HAPPENED,
BECAUSE YOU'RE WITH ME.

408
00:22:00,090 --> 00:22:01,857
- IT'S ALL RIGHT.
- HUH?

409
00:22:01,890 --> 00:22:05,624
- I'M WITH YOU BY CHOICE.

410
00:22:05,657 --> 00:22:07,557
- KAGOME.

411
00:22:23,924 --> 00:22:26,657
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

412
00:23:58,230 --> 00:24:00,296
- DOES TSUBAKI,
THE DARK PRIESTESS,

413
00:24:00,330 --> 00:24:02,230
STILL HAVE THE SACRED JEWEL?

414
00:24:02,263 --> 00:24:05,330
THAT SPELLS TROUBLE.

415
00:24:05,363 --> 00:24:08,863
WAIT--A RED PRIESTESS
AND A WHITE PRIESTESS?

416
00:24:08,896 --> 00:24:10,896
WHO ARE THEY?

417
00:24:10,930 --> 00:24:12,763
TSUBAKI'S HELPERS?

418
00:24:12,796 --> 00:24:15,263
THEY LOOK SO IMPORTANT.

419
00:24:15,296 --> 00:24:16,296
WHAT?

420
00:24:16,330 --> 00:24:18,930
I'M NOT TRICKING KAGOME
AND MIROKU AND THE OTHERS.

421
00:24:18,963 --> 00:24:21,030
THAT'S A LIE!

422
00:24:22,163 --> 00:24:25,096
NEXT TIME, "THE RED
AND WHITE PRIESTESSES."

423
00:24:25,130 --> 00:24:26,130
I'D BETTER LIVE UP
TO MY REPUTATION.

